> Top News Barrett plays finisher as No. 1 Ohio St beats Penn St 38-10 Ohio State quarterback J.T. Barrett, top, celebrates his touchdown against Penn State with teammate Taylor Decker during the first half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Columbus, Ohio. (AP Photo/Paul Vernon)
